title: Wedding
description: The Country Club at Woodmore is a beautiful wedding venue located in Pleasant Prospect Mitchellville, just a few miles from Bowie. The club overlooks the charming Woodmore Lake, making it the ideal location for a wedding ceremony.The main banquet hall at the country club can accommodate at least 250 guests, while the smaller Woodmore rooms can accommodate 50 guests for a rehearsal dinner. Other club amenities include an on-site catering service, an outdoor pool, and a lounge. Outside catering is also permitted.
